Q: 24/7 Jet Inc.在2024年运营的航线中，前五条最繁忙的航线及其飞行次数是多少？
SQL:
SELECT
        a.dep_icao,
        a.arr_icao,
        count(*) AS num
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
        b.supplier_id = "1001"
        AND a.date_month COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci BETWEEN '2024-01'
        AND '2024-12'
GROUP BY
        a.dep_icao,
        a.arr_icao
ORDER BY
        num DESC
        LIMIT 5;
